Php engine for my router

Make sure your index.php contains this settings:

<?php
## Configuration
// Path to engine
$_SERVER['engine']['path'] = "<path-to-engine>";

// Path to pages
$_SERVER['engine']['pages'] = <path-to-pages>;

// Path to script bundles
$_SERVER['engine']['scripts'] = <path-to-scripts-bundles>;

// Default script
$_SERVER['engine']['default_script'] = "<default-script-bundle-name>";

// Path to template
$_SERVER['engine']['template'] = "<path-to-template>";

// Path to css file
$_SERVER['engine']['css'] = "<path-to-css>";

## Run
require_once ($_SERVER['engine']['path']."/engine.php");
?>

JWplayer is required for [video] bbcode!
